metadata.name: For The Memes!
metadata.description:
The fight for decentralisation has never been needed more than now. 6529 needs us to do our part!

For Decentralisation! For the Open Metaverse! For the Memes!

For The Memes! remixes 'SeizeJPGs' by 6529er (card #2) and 'survive in virtuality' by K-art (card #49) from 'The Memes by 6529' collection.
